		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's just a CPLD with the PowerPAK VRC4 fuse-map/verilog/whatever on it. So yes it's "cloned". If you want to own it on a cartridge, go ahead and buy it. It's nothing amazing (technically). It's nice certainly, but not surprising at all. Kid Dracula which also uses VRC4 is also available at RetroZone now and I recommend that game too.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


