<br />People have trouble getting that patch to work because they don't know that they need to patch it with this patch first:
<br />
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.geocities.jp/gx587/ips/fc_gradius2ac_rev022.zip">http://www.geocities.jp/gx587/ips/fc_gr ... rev022.zip</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />
<br />Afterward, find and use the patch found on this blog:
<br />
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://messatu.wordpress.com/">http://messatu.wordpress.com/</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />and it should work.
<br />
<br />Nestopia 1.40 won't play it but FCEUX and Nestopia 1.37 will.

		

