		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">RLError wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Nestopia 1.40 won't play it</div>
<br />This is not a good sign if the ultimate goal is to put the game on a cart. Not that Nestopia is the ultimate almighty emulator or anything (it's pretty good though, from my own personal tests it has almost always behaved the most like the actual hardware), but if the original game works on it and the patched one doesn't, this is a sign that something is wrong. Even if it works on hardware, it might be just unstable enough to break under certain circumstances.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
